Your Home Advantagewith Morgan Stanley
Whether you are buying a home or refinancing your mortgage, Morgan Stanley Private Bank, National Association (the Private Bank) offers a comprehensive suite of residential mortgage products with competitive rates to qualified applicants.





Mortgage OptionsTo Help Achieve Your Goals
Everyone's financial situation and life plans are different. If you qualify, the Private Bank can provide a variety of mortgage options to meet your needs.








CUTTING THROUGHTHE COMPLEXITY
Our team of specialists may identify the best options based on your unique finances and can help guide you from start to finish.
                                    




VARIETY OFFINANCING OPTIONS
Mortgage financing that meets your needs, whether it's your primary residence, vacation getaway, vineyard or other property type.




RELATIONSHIP-BASEDPRICING
Your Morgan Stanley relationship may help you qualify for access to discounted pricing for you or your immediate family members.3




PLEDGED-ASSETFEATURE
The pledged-asset feature may provide the option to pledge eligible securities in your account to replace all or part of a cash down payment for you or a family member.1




CONDITIONALAPPROVAL LETTER
Get clarity on how much you can finance for targeting the right real estate, which ultimately translates into a stronger offer when you're ready to buy.2




COMPREHENSIVEPRODUCT SUITE
Choose from simple to sophisticated mortgages: fixed rate mortgages, a variety of fully amortizing and interest-only adjustable rate mortgages, a 1-Month Libor adjustable rate mortgage and Home Equity Lines of Credit.










